{"tid":2436538,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（Good Luck) 中国深圳東海航空客機機組人員飛行期間毆鬥","createTime":"2021-03-07T08:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T18:23:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4eddd6a17b6633c72b8b50556ebd793185456e11","tid":2436538,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T08:13:43.000Z","msg":"深圳東海航空證實，他們機組人員在飛機上發生糾紛，公司嚴行內部核查，為確保安全運行，涉及人員已第一時間停止工作，公司對由此而產生的不良影響表示誠摯歉意，正全面開展安全整頓，進一步提升運行品質。 <br />\n<br />\n昨日內地網絡流傳消息，指東海航空一架由南通飛往西安的航班，機長與乘務長在飛行期間發生爭執毆打，機長將乘務長手打至骨折，乘務長把機長門牙打掉半顆。深圳民航管理單位約談東海航空。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/25ebea82241e9058026cdf8768d2a351/2021/03/253cca07b7c8e3fd04f8ac28c291252a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2F25ebea82241e9058026cdf8768d2a351%2F2021%2F03%2F253cca07b7c8e3fd04f8ac28c291252a.jpg&h=17042c37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2381946\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2381946&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bCfW%2F3rzywXjCQwsEwiLy3M%3D&h=dc5341a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2381946</a>"},{"pid":"b18096a260a39b77a475f70a804ee58e5cd82a67","tid":2436538,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T08:14:52.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>cockpit困獸鬥</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47ff2b9aec002560570886a21913b605436eec4","tid":2436538,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T08:15:57.000Z","msg":"免費送既<br />\n頭等真人show<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9a4c7449e97165416411180e8abcde5044b66d","tid":2436538,"uid":10890,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T08:16:51.0